{"tid":2038724,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"必須堵截藍絲受惠於外國即將對香港人開啟既後路","createTime":"2020-05-27T17:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T18:17:10.000Z","uid":81236,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe593406ced1cdbc13c24fc88d49e0f8b5380e8","tid":2038724,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1265668742220046339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1265668742220046339&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32VQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=3f59b90c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1265668742220046339&h=84be3353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1265668742220046339</a><br />\n<br />\n已經十分明確表明針對香港但支持香港人<br />\n<br />\n要對政權作出制裁但唔傷及池魚係無咩可能既事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鑑於近日多國動向都係講緊援助香港人方法<br />\n<br />\n有可能為香港人身份開後路<br />\n<br />\n但到時一定大量利字當頭既藍絲衝住去搶<br />\n<br />\n所以大家必須有個方法堵截佢地得益<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大規模，日後一定有審查制度<br />\n<br />\n留/cap低你身邊所知既藍絲既證據，要證明到係佢<br />\n到有審查既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過大家記住千祈唔好觸犯私隱條例呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好犯法就得架啦<br />\n<br />\n唔係要負責<br />\n<br />\n除非你係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff20c767102d8efd3ba40400b56c2f582eda44dd","tid":2038724,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f089ea8706b31db5b48a1fca5ced9c99a34f135d","tid":2038724,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c661cd8aa871b571aaaf7d7022192cc71e5f232f","t